debates threatens more than the league,'' Neuman earlier wrote in a
letter to league members. ``It threatens the voters.''
   Neither the Bush or Dukakis campaigns have said they would
participate in the league-sponsored debates, the first of which is
set for Sept. 8 in Birmingham, Ala.
