   Stock prices drifted lower this morning, as
traders showed little conviction about prospects for the economy,
inflation or interest rates.
   The Dow Jones Average of 30 Industrials, which fell 11.03 on
Friday and 21.52 for the week, was off 0.35 at 2,015.65 at noontime.
