<TEXT>
   Chemical Bank announced an agreement Monday to
sell its Asian private banking operation to Pierson, Heldring &
Pierson NV, a leading Dutch merchant banking concern, for an
undisclosed amount.
   The sale of the unit, based in Hong Kong and Singapore, is
